item.title: ARKANSAS LITTLE LIBRARY PROJECT
item.description: The Arkansas Little Library Project is an organization located in Arkansas, that hopes to place books in locations in Arkansas, that don't have many libraries, books, or content. Or if homeowners and communities don't have a little library and they want one.
